			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=293948">Thurgadin</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Coldian Crossbow</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Coldian Crossbow</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=411648"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:Maestron@luclin.com">Maestron</a> | 
		                        4/19/2001 5:31:39 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">You'll find Lieutenant Ulfur in Thur inside the second gate with the archers up the stairs to the left. He sometimes wanders to the hall on the otherside of the ramparts. Hail him to get the quest.<BR>
 <BR>
Maestron says, 'Hail Lieutenant Ulfur'<BR>
 <BR>
Lieutenant Ulfur says 'Hail, there, Human. How goes it? Much fairer than I, I'll wager. Me troops can't hit the broad side of a mammoth with their crossbows. Oh, by the way, I'm Lieutenant Ulfur, Commander of the 23rd Coldain crossbow regiment, if ye kin call it a regiment. <BR>
 <BR>
You say, 'what regiment?'<BR>
 <BR>
Lieutenant Ulfur says 'Yes, we assist our troops in military endeavors. Although we're almost more harm than good. All me troops have soldier envy, they want in the middle of the rumble, face ta face with their enemies stompin them into the ground. That's all well and good but a contingent of crossbowmen can be the difference in winning or losing. Do you favor ranged weapons, Maestron ? <BR>
 <BR>
Maestron says, 'Yes i favor ranged weapons.'[note: you can just say, &quot;Yes&quot; here.]<BR>
 <BR>
Lieutenant Ulfur says 'Ahh, well, maybe sometime I'll let ya try out one of our famed crossbows. Maybe even give ye one if ye prove yerself to the Coldain cause. Unfortunately, though, we can spare no crossbows now. Perhaps in the future we will be able to. <BR>
 <BR>
At this point neither myself or my friend could not get any more. We tried every possible combination involving &quot;crossbow&quot; and &quot;prove&quot; but to no avail. This may be broken or we may not have the correct phrase.<BR>
 <BR>
Maestron Spellforge<BR>
Level 46 Mage of Luclin
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
